text: Order this on foodpanda. Gotta say the meat is not bad, but portion can be improved. Ordered roast duck + char siew, you would expect is normal roast duck portion, add char siew. Turns out seems like 50% each. Chilli packet like one teaspoon of chilli? Help bro.

Service is really ridiculous it’s not day busy period no one was there the guy who packed my food I asked for black sauce and more chilli I asked for the plastic he simply tell me pour inside my packet rice which ready handed over in the plastic bag. He busy folding plastic bag this not his first time tho. That’s why I putting this up!!! And please could you guys consider bringing rostered chicken rice in.
